Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost, let’s start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really happy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you're always meeting\Nto someone's expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you change to\Nwho you really wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you always have a great smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of only “the beginning,”\NI wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and someday, I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, precious things are never in shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what it is\Nwhen you get it or lose it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,\Nyour uniqueness into strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get lost,\Nlet's start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assassin of the Moonlit Night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we were too late…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa…Sakura…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably fought recklessly…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi Sensei said there was nothing\Nto worry about with the bruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me…Sakura…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy… Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His outward appearance\Nis different, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he’s that guy called Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came into this world, I took the life\Nof the woman some might call my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I could become\Nthe strongest Shinobi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my father brought his Ninjutsu upon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so I became possessed\Nby a Sand Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what he was saying…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s the one who hurt Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey young girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know that\NI’m not the fighting type!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that by looking at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI need to get away from here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and somehow take Sasuke to\Nwhere Kakashi Sensei is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well! Your limit is two shots…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third shot won’t be activated…\NRemember this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to force a Jutsu to activate…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not only will the Jutsu\Nnot properly activate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your Chakra will deplete to zero…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the worst case, you’ll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were to survive,\Nabsolutely nothing good will come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in your case…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the Curse Mark…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let your hatred take over you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rely on the power\Nof the Curse Mark…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your development will stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, you won’t\Nbe able to beat Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI need to get control over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one I failed to kill that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live fighting for only myself\Nand loving myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as long as there are others to kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let’s run! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Sasuke Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she stand\Nin the way of that Gaara…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Darn!\NWhat the heck should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just with him, I don’t want to…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara, Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no use after all…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand gets in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaara…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Lord Kazekage charged me\Nto look after your physical condition
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a member of medical corps\Nand to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not do such things\Nin front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the sand will protect you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashamaru… I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this..? It’s just a scrape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scrape…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit… But it’ll heal in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yashamaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve…never once had a wound so…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered what it’s like…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I explain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like it’s distressing, or difficult…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, to be hit or cut…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should say it’s a feeling\Nof not being able to bear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of not being able to stay normal…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t say it well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I suppose it means a situation\Nthat’s not very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashamaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you dislike me…Yashamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People live their lives while\Nhurting others and while being hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s not so easy for\Npeople to dislike others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yashamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I sort of understand\Nwhat pain is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…maybe I’m injured too?\NThe same as everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always…in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not bleeding, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been having a lot of\Npain around…here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood does flow from a wound\Non the body
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the wound may appear painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as time passes, the pain\Nnaturally disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using medicine,\Nthe healing is even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what’s dangerous is\Na wound of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has more trouble healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wound of the heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wound on the body and\Na wound of the heart are slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a wound on the body,\Nthere is no ointment and sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn’t heal for one’s entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Ncan cure a wound of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is a complicated medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can only be given to you\Nby another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What must I do to…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that can cure\Na wound of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can I get it?\NWhat do I need to do for this pain to be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has already been given to you, Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is…a heart that desires to serve\Na precious person who is close to oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to love and watch over that person,\Njust like my older sister did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that my older sister\Nloved you, Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Spirit Shukaku is a spirit of a living\N person used for the purpose of attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sand which automatically tries to\Nprotect you is like the love of a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that sand is filled\Nwith your mother’s will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister…probably wanted to\Nprotect you even more after dying…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashamaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for what you did earlier…\Nfor stopping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a precious person\Nwho is near me, Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you understand…my pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes like iron…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaf…Hurricane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many did you take\Ndown Kakashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, it seems I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my twenty-third.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That poser attitude of yours\Nstill makes you cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the reason you are my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Let’s go! 					– All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yashamaru…\NI have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some ointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about earlier…\Nlt must’ve hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home…freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful, you brat--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Again… 					– Go home, freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--? What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s…it’s Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This guy's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought… Things don’t go well…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it…that only I’m such a freak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that can cure\Na wound of the heart is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why me…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why always me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who…? Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done…Gaara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yashamaru…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s those eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?\NWeren’t you gonna run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these two…to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-These two are…my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try laying so much as\Nanother finger on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll clobber you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…what’s the matter?!\NWeren’t you gonna clobber me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and come at me…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\Nlt’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, breathe in the air\NLift your face to the sky and jump
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:22:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it rains, take a break\NGo where the wind takes you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many regrets\NDon’t let this scar be for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go carve the badges in our chest\NYes, it’s Show Time, life begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone makes mistakes\N It’s nothing to be ashamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t let this scar be for naught\NWalk with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform sadness into the wind\Nand continue to forge on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forge on strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this guy’s strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may seem like a senseless\Nweakling to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…what’s…?\NWhat’s this feeling welling up inside me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know,\Nbut I just don’t want to lose to this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “Light vs. Dark:\NThe Two Faces of Gaara”
